@sc{Mediatex} uses @sc{Exim4} 
(@pxref{Top,,, spec, Specification of the Exim Mail Transfer Agent})
to send mails so as to notify @actor{Actor}s.
Please configure Exim (or any other mail agent) so as your host can
send mails.

